INSERT INTO
    trips (
    start_vessel_event_id,end_vessel_event_id,first_arrival,trip_assembler_id,fiskeridir_vessel_id,landing_coverage,period,period_extended,start_precision_id,end_precision_id,start_precision_direction,end_precision_direction,trip_precision_status_id,period_precision,distance,distancer_id,start_port_id,end_port_id,position_layers_status,track_coverage,trip_position_cargo_weight_distribution_status,trip_position_fuel_consumption_distribution_status
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::BIGINT[],$2::BIGINT[],$3::TIMESTAMPTZ[],$4::INT[],$5::BIGINT[],$6::tstzrange[],$7::tstzrange[],$8::tstzrange[],$9::INT[],$10::INT[],$11::TEXT[],$12::TEXT[],$13::INT[],$14::tstzrange[],$15::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$16::INT[],$17::TEXT[],$18::TEXT[],$19::INT[],$20::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$21::INT[],$22::INT[]
    )
         RETURNING trip_id AS "trip_id!:TripId",period AS "period!:PgRange<DateTime<Utc>>",landing_coverage AS "landing_coverage!:PgRange<DateTime<Utc>>",fiskeridir_vessel_id AS "fiskeridir_vessel_id!:FiskeridirVesselId"
